<br>
Rhombus - I look forward to seeing this expansion, as well. But, in order to make it appealing, aside from the actual adventure of undertaking it, there has to be some draw, or material incentive? Moral incentives are largely ineffective, no matter how altruistic the audience is. So, if it's not much higher experience, or much better loot, or, a different risk vs. reward model (which is my prediction), what might it be?<br>
<br>
Great discussion, by the way.<br>
